Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.57,0:00:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,翻译 饼干一枚 右翼部鸣明 校对 牙牙 Husky Linn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,时间轴 SG 文本处理 谷子 yoyo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,资源搬运 yoyo 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.49,0:00:28.96,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,俺们到啦！~\NWe're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:32.96,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,果然只有亲自来北方才能体会到这种美啊\NThe great north is so beautiful in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:34.81,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,等下 等下 呆在那别动\NWait, wait, stay right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:39.07,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好啦 笑一个\NAll right, smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:40.63,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好 现在做出你们\NOkay, now one where it looks like
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:42.30,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,在找怪物的样子\Nyou're looking for a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.47,0:00:45.67,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不错 现在做出像是在讲笑话的样子\NOkay, now one like you made a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:49.98,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,行 那么现在 做出那个笑话咋一听不那么好笑\NOkay, now, do one where the joke's not that funny,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:53.58,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但是要想一会才get到笑点的样子\Nbut it's more like a joke that makes you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:00:56.62,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好啦 我认为差不多也照够了吧\NOkay, I think that's enough photography.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:00:58.39,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但这可是康妮小天使的第一次任务啊\NBut it's Connie's first mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:00.95,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她的父母让我多拍点照片回来\NHer parents asked me to take lots of pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:03.12,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,非常感谢您能够让我\NThank you so much for letting me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.13,0:01:04.81,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,参与这个任务 珍珠\Ncome on this mission, Pearl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:07.56,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,很荣幸能和您一起工作\NIt's such an honor to work alongside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:09.86,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦 康妮 你的剑术水平 \NWell, Connie, your sword-fighting skills
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.87,0:01:12.27,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,已经远远超过我所期望的了\Nhave far exceeded my expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.27,0:01:14.87,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,再加上我小心的教导\N And, with my careful supervision, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:16.50,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我当然可以相信你能够轻松搞定\NI'm confident that you can handle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:18.77,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这样一个简单的宝石修复任务\Na simple gem-recovery mission like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:20.47,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,太感谢您了\NThank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.48,0:01:22.71,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我保证我绝对不会让您失望！老师！\NI promise I won't let you down, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:27.18,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,康妮第一次任务唔嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷\NConnie's first mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:31.02,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,复述一遍任务目标，康妮\NRecap the mission for us, Connie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:34.29,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,石榴感觉到了一些堕转的宝石在这森林里浪得很嗨\NGarnet sensed some corrupted gem activity in these woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.29,0:01:35.82,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,而我们的任务就是找到它们的位置\NIt is our job to locate it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:38.01,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,解决掉它们并用泡泡收容\Ndestabilize its form and bubble it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:39.13,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,非常不错\NVery good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.13,0:01:40.71,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你的人类身体无法\NNow, your human bodies aren't designed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:42.05,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,适应严寒\Nto last in this cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.05,0:01:43.83,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,所以我们必须要特别小心\Nso we'll have to be extra careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:46.18,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那没问题 我的背包里已经装满了\NThat's okay. I've got this backpack filled
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:48.69,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,能让我们在这个鸟不拉屎的地方多活一会儿的东西\Nwith everything we need to survive in the wilderness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.69,0:01:51.36,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我还带来三国杀以免我们无聊\NAnd I brought board games in case we get bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:53.51,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,啊 可以 很不错\NAh, yes. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:57.44,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,所以，我们该怎么知道这些损坏了的宝石在附近？\NSo, how will we know if this corrupted gem is nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:01.35,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,就是这么知道的 它来了\NThat's how! Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:09.86,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,记住，你们要一起战斗\NRemember, you work together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:12.33,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗 康妮 准备好了 史蒂文\NReady, Connie? Ready, Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:18.63,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,居然有两只\NTwo of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:23.30,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,史蒂文 泡泡辅助\NSteven, bubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:24.30,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,泡泡防护罩\NBubble power!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:32.01,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,它们…跑路了\NThey...ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:34.11,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,本来不应该有两只才对\NThere weren't supposed to be two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:35.95,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,噢 噢-- 我有个主意\NOh, oh -- I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:37.58,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们可以分头行动\NWe could split up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.09,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你可以去跟踪他们中的其中一只 珍珠\NYou can go after one of them, Pearl,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.62,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,而我和史蒂文去跟踪另一只\Nand Steven and I will go after the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:43.66,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,康妮 你是我的学生\NConnie, you are my pupil,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:46.03,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,所以我清楚你的战斗技术很优秀\Nso I know your combat skills are excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:48.16,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但是我担心这样太冒险了\NBut I'm afraid this is too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.56,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你们之前还没有参加过真正的战斗\NYou've never been in a real fight before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:52.07,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嗯 但那并不是真的\NWell, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:54.13,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,康妮在医院和那些泼猴般的宝石大战过\NConnie defeated those gem experiments at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:55.00,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但--\NBut--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:56.10,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,还有你看\NAnd look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:57.57,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我带了这些对讲机\NI brought these walkie-talkies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:59.54,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这样如果出现意外 我们可以互相联系\Nso we can talk to each other in case something happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.18,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,可--\NBut--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:04.85,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我已经在之前已经读了这本书至少20次 \N（《如何在大自然的野蛮怀抱中生存》）\NAnd I've read this book front to back, at least 20 times![HOW TO SURVIVE    The punishment of nature]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.62,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那好吧\NWell, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:13.02,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但是一会儿一旦找到了怪物，就要立刻联系我\NBut as soon as you find the monster, contact me immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:15.16,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我不想你们独自与那玩意战斗\NI don't want you fighting this thing alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:17.52,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,再问一次，你们要找到什么\NOne more time, what are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.73,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,怪兽\N A monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.26,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,找到它后你们会做什么\NWhat do you do when you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.60,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,联系你\NCall you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.03,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,谁是你们最喜欢的宝石战士\NAnd who's your favorite gem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:24.50,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,珍珠啦啦啦啦\NPearl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.13,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哎呀 谢谢啦\NWhy, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:29.80,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那么 注意安全\NNow, be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:31.07,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,是的 长官\N Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:39.91,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们现在要做的就是跟着这些脚印\NAll we have to do is follow these tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:44.89,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不错 这些都是新鲜的\NYeah. These are fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:47.97,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们跟踪它直到它停下来休息为止\NWe trail it until it stops to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:50.56,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哇 康妮 你简直是贝爷第二\NWow, Connie, you're a wilderness expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:52.48,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦 我喜欢事先准备好一切\NWell, I like to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:55.20,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,当文明崩溃 世界终结之时\NWhen civilization collapses and this world ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:57.73,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我需要准备好创造一个新的世界\NI need to be ready to build the new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:00.07,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,是啊 我猜如果地球被母星侵略的话\NYeah, I guess if homeworld invades Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:02.44,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,事态对人类来说会非常失控\Nthings could get pretty crazy for humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:03.90,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,别管宝石了\NForget gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:07.44,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,人类已经迎来了他们自己造成的末日\NHumans are already starting their own demise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:09.11,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,石油危机啊 史蒂文真主\NPeak oil, Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:11.08,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,吾等该如何解决这祸灾\NHow do we handle terminal decline
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:13.68,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,而不需要备用能源\Nwithout alternate energy sources?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.62,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你俩在做什么\NHow are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:17.78,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你们饿了吗\NAre you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:20.35,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,别忘了 你们人类是需要吃东西的\NRemember,you humans need to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:21.49,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,是的 长官\NYes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:24.22,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,还好我装备了好多哒生存‘燃料’\NLuckily, I packed plenty of survival fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:26.49,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,士力架，横扫饥饿，做回自己\N Time to get our protein on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:32.00,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,还好这里刚下了雪\NGood thing this snow is here --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:34.47,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这样更方便我们追踪怪兽\Nit makes following tracks a lot easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:36.20,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,当然\NI'll say!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:39.41,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,所以这些堕转的宝石就像野生动物\NSo, these corrupted gems are like wild animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:41.98,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,只有一些战斗和逃跑的条件反射\NJust a bundle of fight or flight reflexes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:43.61,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,以及生存本能\Nand survival instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:47.15,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,唔嗯 他们现在是这样 但是之前的他们不是\NWell, they're like that now, but before they were different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:50.22,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,他们曾经是正常的宝石人 就像珍珠 紫晶和石榴一样\NThey used to be normal gems like Pearl, Amethyst, and Garnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:54.86,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,他们也拥有思想和感觉，朋友……\NThey had thoughts and feelings, friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:56.89,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我不知道堕转对它们来说是怎么样的\NI don't really know how the corruption works.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:58.39,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,大概像是生病了一样\NIt's like they're sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.69,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她们不记得自己以前是谁\NThey don't remember who they used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:01.90,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,也许她们连自己原来\NMaybe they don't even know
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.60,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,长什么样都忘记了\Nhow to look like themselves anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:06.03,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你还好吧\NYou okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:07.93,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嗯 我没事\NYeah, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:10.54,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,噢 我知道怎样可以让我换个心情了\NOh, I know what'll cheer me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:22.98,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,史蒂文 康妮\NSteven, Connie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:25.35,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我完全失去这只怪兽的踪迹了\NI'm not having any luck finding this monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:28.06,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,也许我们应该回到神庙重新编队\NWe might have to return to the temple and regroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:29.99,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不 不用 我们可以搞定的\NNo, no! We can handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:31.96,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,现在进展非常顺利\NWe're making great progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:34.33,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们完全可以自己解决\NWe can definitely take care of this ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:37.23,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘛 好吧 你听起来挺自信的\NOh, well, you sound very confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:39.60,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那就继续任务吧 还有记住了 康妮\NCarry on then,and remember, Connie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:43.00,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,打开步伐 压低重心 我都记得的 老师\NStance wide, body lowered. I've got it, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:45.61,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,平衡即是关键\N♪ Balance is the key ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:48.91,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-需要帮忙吗  -是的 谢谢\NNeed some help there?Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:57.10,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哇 看看这些脚印\NWhoa. Look at the tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.94,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哇\NWhoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.36,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,看这一团乱七八糟的痕迹\NNow, this is a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:04.36,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,其中的一些看起来像人的脚印\NSome of these prints look humanoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:06.33,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,珍珠来过这里吗\NCould pearl have been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:08.56,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但是珍珠往另一个方向走了\NBut Pearl went the other direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:13.53,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,怪兽的…人的…怪兽的\NMonster...humanoid... monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:15.79,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这意味着什么呢\NWhat could this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:19.46,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们应该搭建一个躲避暴风雪的庇护所\NWe should probably take shelter from this blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:22.58,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但是首先 要先收集一些松针\NBut first, let's grab some of these pine needles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:25.50,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们可以用它来泡一些富含维C的茶\NWe can brew a vitamin-C-rich tea with them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:27.05,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这样我们就不会得败血病\Nso we don't get scurvy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.42,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,就像海盗一样\NLike a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:36.06,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,茶泡好了\NThe tea's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.64,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,来 尝一下\NHere, try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:38.48,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:41.80,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,味道如何\NHow is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:43.18,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,很\NIt's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.85,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,很难喝\NIt's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:47.07,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,当然了\NWell, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:48.99,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好不好喝不重要\NIt's not about tasting good, Steven,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:51.99,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,重要的是在大自然的惩罚下生存下来\Nit's about surviving the punishment of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:59.11,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,所以说 为什么那里会有人的脚印\NSo, why were there humanoid tracks out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:02.12,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那不是我们的 也不是珍珠的\NThey weren't ours, and they weren't Pearl's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:04.15,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,更不可能是怪兽的\NIt couldn't have been the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:07.00,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,除非是一个装扮成怪兽的人\NUnless it's just some guy in a monster suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:09.01,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但那种事只在动画片里发生\NBut that kind of thing only happens in cartoons,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:11.34,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,而且通常是因财产纠纷引发的\Nusually over a property dispute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:14.38,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,也许就是一个装扮成怪兽的人呢\NMaybe it is a guy in a monster costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:15.35,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你也这么认为？\NYou think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:16.80,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,当然不是同意字面上的意思了 傻瓜 \NI don't mean literally, silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:19.80,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我的意思是也许在那怪兽的外表之下\NWhat I mean is there might be a conscious gem
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:21.47,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,还有一个神志清醒的宝石人\Nstill inside there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:22.80,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这可能吗\NIs that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:25.56,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,也许它还在怪兽与原型之间\NWhat if the monster is turning back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:26.89,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不断转换\Ninto its original form.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:29.39,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,如果真是那样 也许它还没有像我们认为的那样彻底堕转\NIf it is, it might not be as corrupted as we think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:31.48,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们可能还有机会拯救它\NThere might still be a chance to save it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:32.61,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,怎么救\NHow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:34.65,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我不能治愈堕转的宝石人--\NI can't heal gems that are corrupted --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:36.03,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,起码不能治愈完全堕转的\Nat least not all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:38.40,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但是如果它没有完全堕转…\NBut if it's half-corrupted...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.49,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这边\NThis way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.53,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘘\NShh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:57.09,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,它看起来很害怕 是在害怕我们吗\NIt seems scared. Is it running from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:08:00.21,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,如果它是在害怕…它自己呢\NWhat if it's running... from itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:02.39,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘘 小声点\NShh!\ Keep your voice down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:04.90,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你们好啊\NHello, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.48,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那里进展如何\NHow's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.93,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,天气真的变得越来越恶劣了\NThis weather has really taken a turn for the worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:10.18,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我可不想为\Nand I would hate to be responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:12.02,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你们陷入的危险负责\Nfor putting you two in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.39,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,确保你们穿得 --\NMake sure you bundle up with--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:16.11,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-史蒂文 快关掉 -我正在关呢\NSteven! Turn it off! I'm trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:18.39,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,噢 还有 别忘了 如果你们找到了怪兽\NOh! And, remember, if you find the monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:21.41,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,千万不要发出任何惊天动地的声音\Ndon't make any loud, startling noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:23.73,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-喂 在吗 -这天杀的手套怎么这么滑\NHello?! Anyone there?!Stupid,slipper mittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:26.33,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你们不回答 我就继续说啦\NI'm just going to keep talking until somebody answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:27.95,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,史蒂文\NSteven!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:33.92,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,等下 让我先试试与它交流\NWait. Let me try talking to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.59,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘿 你好吗\NHey. How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.58,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呃 你能听懂我吗\NUm, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.75,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你还清醒吗\NAre you in there somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:43.43,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你可以控制住的\NYou can control this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:46.05,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,快想起你以前是谁\NRemember who you used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:48.72,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,史蒂文 我不觉得有用\NSteven, I don't think it's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:59.23,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,史蒂文\NSteven!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:04.12,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘿 看这儿\NHey! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:08.96,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,康妮 你在干什么\NConnie,what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:10.94,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我…\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:12.50,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:15.17,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我还没有准备好\NI...wasn't prepared for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:18.28,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,史蒂文 康妮\N Steven, Connie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:20.67,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你们不说话是因为我问的“你最喜欢的宝石战士”吗\NIs this because of the "favorite gem" thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:23.14,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哈 那只是开玩笑而已啦\NHeh, that was just a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:24.79,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,千万别告诉石榴\NDon't tell garnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.23,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,康妮\NConnie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:30.40,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,珍珠 我们找到怪兽了\NPearl, we found the monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:31.98,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-啥 -我们需要支援\NWhat?! We need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:33.48,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我马上过来 康妮\NI'll be right there,Connie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:38.36,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那是谁\NWho's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:40.41,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,防-防-防-防-防-防御\NB-B-B-B-B-B-Bubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:01.16,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,铁石英 那些脚印\NJasper. Those footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.35,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那些怪物是在害怕她\NThe monsters were running from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:05.55,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,康妮 怪兽在 --\NConnie, where's the --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:06.63,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,铁石英\NJasper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:14.01,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘿 玫瑰 看我抓到了什么\NHey, Rose, look what I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:25.37,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你俩没事吧\NAre you two okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:27.45,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嗯 我们没事\NYeah, we're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:29.79,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,噢 谢天谢地\NOh, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:31.16,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,真是一场灾难\NWhat a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:33.04,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,要是当初我知道铁石英也在这儿\NI never would have let you come on this mission
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.96,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,就不会让你参与这次任务\Nif I knew Jasper would be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:36.70,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-对不起  -啊？\NI'm sorry. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:39.75,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我以为我已经做好了战斗的准备 但其实我没有\NI thought I'd be ready to fight, but I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:41.05,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我失败了\NI failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:42.67,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我本来就没让你战斗\NYou weren't supposed to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:45.04,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我只让你联系我 而你也这么做了\NYou were supposed to call me, and you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.34,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你完全成功了\NThis was a total success.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:49.26,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,康妮的首次任务\NConnie's first mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:51.06,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,康妮的首次任务\NConnie's first mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:52.38,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,来张合照\NGroup picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:53.81,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,史蒂文\NSteven!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:55.27,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,噢 又要拍照\NOh. Another picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:56.27,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,当你要拍了就告--\NTell me when you--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:57.93,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,拍好了\NEh, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.52,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,噢 不\NOh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:01.22,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你的爸妈会看见这个吗\NAre your parents going to see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.24,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我的爸妈会看我所有的照片\NMy parents see all of my photos, ma'am.
